window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A witch and her husband rescue a toymaker in the woods, but this is no ordinary fairy tale…</p> <p>While most Lukoi spend their days preparing for a long, dangerous winter, Micah Firekeeper is a toymaker. He lives alone in his great-grandmother’s cottage, making beautiful designs full of color and life. When a fire destroys his home and all of his creations, Micah is taken in by Viv and Sasha, a married couple who live in the underground Compound. </p> <p>Viv is a witch, and she sees in Micah a kindred spirit. Sasha is a submissive who loves deeply and finds joy in small pleasures, and between his exuberance and Viv’s compassion, Micah begins to forge a new life. But as autumn approaches, something sinister stirs in the woods, and Micah, Viv, and Sasha will have to band together to protect what they hold dear.</p> <p><i>Autumn of the Witch</i> is a polyam romance featuring m/m/f, m/m, and m/f scenes.</p>"; 
